title: Dick's Kitchen
typeOfFood: Vegan-friendly, Lacto, Ovo, American, Beer/Wine, Non-veg
description: Serves meat, veg options available. The menu has vegetarian dishes, vegan sides - including the tempeh reuben with vegan cheese and Luna and coconut ice cream milkshakes. Many items are house-made and those that aren't are purchased from local producers or farms. The atmosphere is open and airy like a diner in NYC.
